description.en: BITFXT coin is the official loyalty token for bitfxt exchange. It can be used to pay for any service fees withing the exchange including listing fee, trading fee, casting of votes, and for trading as a base currency in bitfxt exchange. Users can earn more coins by trading on bitfxt exchange, referring new traders and for holding/staking bitfxt coin on the exchange.
